20means%20your%20options%20are%20flying%20from%20LaGuardia%2C%20or%20switching%20your%20Newark%20layover%20to%20another%20United%20hub.%20United%20doesn't%20fly%20from%20JFK.%20You'd%20have%20to%20reroute%20via%20DC%2C%20Houston%2C%20Chicago%2C%20or%20Denver.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESay%2C%20for%20example%2C%20you're%20flying%20some%20regional%20city%20to%20Europe%20via%20Newark.%20Call%20United%20and%20ask%20to%20be%20rerouted%20via%20one%20of%20the%20other%20hubs.%20They%20have%20loads%20of%20international%20flying%20from%20up%20and%20down%20the%20East%20Coast%20and%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20country.%20Right%20now%2C%20their%20policy%20is%20scheduled%20flights%20between%20May%206%20and%20May%2023%20(booked%20before%20May%204)%20can%20change%20their%20flight%20for%20free%20(no%20change%20fee%20or%20fare%20difference).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flight%20must%20be%20between%20the%20same%20two%20cities%20(or%20from%20either%20LaGuardia%20or%20Philadelphia)%2C%20be%20the%20same%20cabin%2C%20and%20be%202%20days%20before%20or%20after%20the%20original%20flight%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.united.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Ffly%2Ftravel%2Ftrip-planning%2Ftravel-alerts.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etheir%20policy%20says%3C%2Fa%3E.%20If%20you're%20flying%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspirit-cutting-12-000-flights-making-summer-travel-harder-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpirit%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20another%20non-United%20airline%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20call%20to%20see%20your%20options%20about%20changing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20to%20a%20book%20a%20future%20flight%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20going%20through%20a%20different%20airport%20altogether%2C%20or%20making%20sure%20your%20Newark%20layover%20is%20long%20because%20the%20delays%20are%20not%20just%20out%20of%20Newark%20but%20into%20Newark%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20your%20life%20easier%20if%20you%20%3Cem%3Eare%3C%2Fem%3E%20flying%20through%20Newark%2C%20%3Ca%2