of%20power%20sources.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EDuring%20an%20emergency%2C%20you%20may%20have%20to%20be%20on%20the%20move%2C%20so%20your%20radio%20must%20go%20with%20you.%20The%20best%20emergency%20radios%20are%20easy%20to%20carry%20and%20can%20fit%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fgo-bag-supplies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ego-bag%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EWhen%20you%E2%80%99re%20bugging%20out%2C%20your%20radio%20is%20likely%20to%20get%20banged%20up.%20It%20should%20be%20able%20to%20withstand%20getting%20tossed%20around%20a%20bit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Many%20emergency%20radios%20serve%20as%20an%20all-in-one%20survival%20tool.%20Common%20extras%20include%20a%20flashlight%20with%20SOS%20signaling%20and%20a%20power%20bank%20for%20charging%20your%20phone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22342e74e1-98a2-41bb-9347-de94e0facb2f%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20overall%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20overall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20each%20Midland%20radio%20has%20its%20use%2C%20my%20favorite%20was%20the%20ER310.%20This%20heavy-duty%20powerhouse%20is%20a%20beefier%20emergency%20solution%20with%20versatile%20power%20options%3A%20hand%20crank%2C%20rechargeable%20Li-ion%20battery%2C%20solar%20charging%2C%20and%20battery%20backup%20using%20AA%20batteries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20design%20is%20remarkably%20similar%20to%20the%20more%20portable%20ER210%2C%20but%20only%20the%20ER310%20is%20about%2030%25%20larger%20and%20more%20durable.%20When%20I%20dropped%20it%20onto%20cement%2C%20it%20just%20turned%20off%3B%20no%20pieces%20broke%20off%2C%20and%20it%20functioned%20fine%20afterward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20my%20measurement%2C%20the%20flashlight%20was%20brighter%20(55%20lux%20for%20the%20ER310%20versus%2040%20lux%20for%20the%20ER210).%20It%20has%20the%20same%20SOS%20flash%20mode%20but%20also%20adds%20an%20ultrasonic%20dog%20whistle%20to%20aid%20a%20rescue%20team%20in%20finding%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fembed%2FPoAd1rj9qgav4OvU2l%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rechargeable%20battery%20was%20impressive%2C%20powering%20the%20unit%20for%207.5%20hours%20on%20top%20volume%20and%20brightest%20light%2C%20and%20it%20recharged%20in%20six%20hours%20using%20a%20wall%20outlet.%20I%20was%20less%20impressed%20with%20hand-crank%20charging.%20I%20only%20got%2010%20minutes%20of%20use%20after%20a%20minute%20of%20cranking%2C%20but%20the%20solar%20charging%20was%20better%2C%20though%20it%20has%20the%20same%20solar%20and%20device%20charging%20limitations%20as%20the%20ER210.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmidlandusa.com%2Fproducts%2Fer210-compact-emergency-crank-wx-radio%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMidland%20addresses%20this%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20product%20page%E2%80%99s%20FAQs%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20solar%20charging%20is%20meant%20to%20extend%20the%20charge%20of%20the%20radio%2C%20but%20not%20fully%20charge%20it.%20For%20best%20results%2C%20fully%20charge%20the%20radio%20via%20the%20USB%2C%20and%20then%20place%20it%20in%20a%20sunny%20spot.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20product%20page%20addresses%20another%20limitation%3A%20device%20charging.%20The%20ER310%20has%20a%20USB%20port%20for%20charging%20devices.%20However%2C%20it%20would%20start%20charging%20my%20phone%20or%20laptop%2C%20then%20stop%20after%20a%20minute%20or%20two.%20The%20company%20states%20that%20the%20ER310%20was%20created%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20and%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20designed%20to%20charge%20today%E2%80%99s%20phones.%20Instead%20of%20relying%20on%20the%20ER310%20to%20charge%20your%20devices%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20want%20to%20keep%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-portable-chargers-power-banks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eportable%20power%20bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20your%20emergency%20supplies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Someone%20holds%20the%20Midland%20ER310%20emergency%20radio%20in%20their%20hand%20outside.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e2fafc6ad288d148085b4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221255%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWhen%20enough%20sunlight%20is%20hitting%20the%20ER310%20for%20it%20to%20charge%2C%20the%20red%20light%20between%20the%20lightning%20symbol%20and%20Band%20illuminates.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ER310%E2%80%99s%20audio%20clarity%20and%20loudness%20were%20closer%20to%20those%20of%20the%20WR120%2C%20though%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20three%20radios%20were%20negligible.%20Most%20people%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20notice%20the%20five-decibel%20difference%20between%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ER310%20is%20the%20only%20model%20I%20used%20in%20an%20emergency%20scenario%2C%20and%20it%20worked%20like%20a%20charm.%20When%20the%20National%20Weather%20Service%20issued%20a%20tornado%20warning%20for%20my%20county%2C%20the%20radio%E2%80%99s%20siren%20went%20off%20loudly%2C%20and%20the%20flashlight%20started%20flashing%20on%20and%20off.%20It%20was%20startling%2C%20but%20that%E2%80%99s%20what%20you%20want%20in%20an%20emergency.%20We%20immediately%20received%20the%20details%20and%20guidance%20from%20our%20local%20weather%20channel.%20It%20helped%20keep%20us%20informed%20while%20my%20family%20huddled%20in%20the%20basement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20power%2C%20flexibility%2C%20and%20durability%20matter%20more%20than%20portability%2C%20the%20ER310%20is%20our%20pick%20for%20emergency%20preparedness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223f09939f-8ff8-477e-9e93-07ccab28a9dd%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20basic%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20basic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Midland%20WR120%20is%20a%20stationary%20weather%20alert%20system%20in%20your%20home.%20While%20other%20emergency%20radios%20offer%20AM%2FFM%20bands%2C%20this%20radio%20exclusively%20provides%20weather%20information%20through%20the%20NOAA%20broadcasts.%20The%20WR120%20relies%20on%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.weather.gov%2Farx%2Fsame%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAME%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20localized%20programming%3A%20Just%20enter%20your%20county%2C%20and%20you%E2%80%99ll%20get%20alerts%20that%20apply%20to%20your%20area.%20You%20can%20also%20program%20it%20for%20up%20to%2025%20other%20counties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WR120%20alerts%20you%20to%20floods%2C%20tornadoes%2C%20civil%20danger%20warnings%2C%20thunderstorms%2C%20hurricanes%2C%20and%20over%2060%20other%20emergencies%20and%20weather%20hazards.%20The%20alert%E2%80%99s%20severity%20%E2%80%94%20advisory%2C%20watch%2C%20or%20warning%20%E2%80%94%20is%20displayed%20on%20the%20radio.%20You%20can%20also%20customize%20your%20alerts%20by%20choosing%20from%20alert%20tones%20with%20three%20loudness%20levels.%20The%20radio%20doubles%20as%20an%20alarm%20clock%20and%20is%20backlit%20for%20visibility%20in%20the%20dark.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Midland%20WR120%20weather%20radio%20is%20displayed%20on%20an%20old%20chest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e321da466d2b74ab5895d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221255%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Midland%20WR120%20handles%20weather%20radio%20exclusively.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20the%20other%20Midland%20radios%20in%20this%20roundup%2C%20the%20WR120%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20flashlight%20or%20rechargeable%20battery%2C%20though%20it%20has%20battery%20backup%20for%20power%20outages.%20I%20tested%20the%20reception%20in%20my%20basement%20and%20the%20sound%20clarity%20at%20its%20maximum%20volume%20(79%20decibels).%20The%20reception%20was%20sometimes%20fuzzy%2C%20but%20I%20had%20no%20trouble%20understanding%20what%20was%20being%20communicated.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20WR120%20is%20mainly%20powered%20by%20a%20wall%20outlet%2C%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20test%20its%20portability%20or%20durability.%20However%2C%20it%20performed%20its%20job%20as%20intended.%20It%20alerted%20me%20during%20the%20weekly%20NOAA%20weather%20alert%20test%2C%20and%20it%20just%20sat%20quietly%20on%20my%20shelf%20when%20not%20sending%20alerts%2C%20though%20it%20was%20fun%20to%20press%20the%20Weather%20button%20now%20and%20then%20to%20get%20the%20forecast.%20This%20is%20a%20solid%20option%20for%20folks%20who%20want%20a%20simple%20at-home%20way%20to%20get%20weather%20alerts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223714a1ed-8a27-4b49-9f6f-fbff0aed786b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20portable%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBest%20portable%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ER210%20is%20Midland%E2%80%99s%20versatile%20emergency%20radio%2C%20built%20for%20everyday%20use%20and%20crisis%20situations.%20It%E2%80%99s%20equipped%20with%20three%20charging%20options%3A%20a%20rechargeable%20lithium-ion%20battery%2C%20a%20hand%20crank%2C%20and%20solar.%20I%20was%20most%20impressed%20with%20the%20hand%20crank%20option.%20After%20just%20one%20minute%20of%20cranking%2C%20the%20radio%20ran%20for%20three%20hours%20on%20top%20volume%20with%20the%20flashlight%20on%20its%20brightest%20setting.%20For%20reference%2C%20the%20fully%20charged%20Li-ion%20battery%20lasted%20six%20hours%20and%20took%20roughly%20six%20hours%20to%20charge%20from%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20this%20is%20the%20smallest%20of%20the%20three%20Midland%20radios%20I%20tested%2C%20it's%20packed%20with%20features%2C%20including%20NOAA%20weather%20scanning%20across%20all%20seven%20weather%20channels%2C%20SOS%20mode%20for%20the%20flashlight%2C%20and%20a%20loud%20siren%20and%20flashing%20lights%20when%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20weather%20alert%20near%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221673%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20MIdland%20ER210%20emergency%20radio%20is%20displayed%20on%20the%20rim%20of%20a%20fire%20pit.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e39f7a466d2b74ab58b5f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221255%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20compact%20size%20of%20the%20Midland%20ER210%20makes%20it%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20staying%20informed%20on%20the%20go.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20impressed%20with%20the%20ER210's%20sound%20quality.%20It%20had%20the%20clearest%20reception%20of%20the%20three%20and%20was%20also%20the%20loudest%20at%2083%20decibels.%20The%20durability%20was%20impressive%20but%20not%20perfect.%20I%20dropped%20it%20from%20a%20height%20of%207%20feet%20onto%20cement%2C%20and%20the%20solar%20panel%20popped%20off%2C%20revealing%20the%20radio%E2%80%99s%20innards.%20Other%20than%20this%20cosmetic%20issue%2C%20everything%20functioned%20fine%20after%20the%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ER210%20has%20a%20few%20weak%20spots.%20The%20solar%20charging%20underwhelmed%20me.%20I%20love%20that%20the%20charging%20light%20comes%20on%20when%20the%20sun%20is%20charging%20it%2C%20but%20after%20two%20hours%20in%20the%20sun%2C%20it%20only%20provides%20a%20few%20minutes%20of%20radio%20broadcasting.%20It%20was%20also%20ineffective%20at%20charging%20my%20phone%20via%20USB.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20cons%2C%20the%20ER210%20is%20an%20excellent%20compact%20solution%20for%20tracking%20what%E2%80%99s%20happening%20during%20an%20emergency.%20Its%20size%20and%20weight%20make%20it%20great%20for%20tossing%20into%20your%20everyday%20carry%20or%20bug-out%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e6c472cc-62bd-4c89-bda9-3f1116b93782%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20emergency%20radios%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReception%20and%20sound%20quality%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20took%20the%20radios%20to%20my%20basement%2C%20where%20the%20reception%20is%20poor%2C%20and%20tuned%20them%20to%20the%20same%20stations%20(AM%2FFM%2FNOAA)%20to%20compare%20the%20sound%20quality.%20I%20also%20cranked%20them%20to%20their%20highest%20volume%20and%20used%20a%20decibel%20meter%20to%20measure%20how%20loud%20they%20got.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWeather%20alerts%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20my%20area%2C%20the%20weekly%20NOAA%20weather%20alert%20test%20is%20at%2011%3A15%20a.m.%20each%20Wednesday.%20I%20set%20up%20each%20radio%20to%20sound%20the%20alarm%20when%20this%20test%20was%20going%20on.%20I%20also%20lucked%20out%20during%20testing%20and%20was%20under%20tornado%20and%20severe%20thunderstorm%20warnings%2C%20which%20also%20triggered%20the%20alert%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPower%20options%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20tested%20all%20the%20radios'%20power%20options.%20If%20the%20radio%20had%20a%20rechargeable%20battery%2C%20I%20timed%20how%20long%20it%20took%20to%20charge%20from%20empty%20to%20full%20using%20a%20wall%20outlet.%20To%20test%20solar%2C%20I%20timed%20how%20long%20the%20radio%20and%20flashlight%20ran%20after%20two%20hours%20of%20solar%20charging.%20For%20the%20hand%20crank%2C%20I%20cranked%20the%20depleted%20radio%20for%20one%20minute%20and%20timed%20how%20long%20the%20flashlight%20and%20radio%20ran.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fembed%2F74tNZqvq1g7bci2Oco%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ERuntime%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20evaluated%20how%20long%20the%20radios%20ran%20from%20fully%20charged%20until%20empty%20when%20I%20blasted%20the%20radio%20at%20high%20volume%20and%20shone%20the%20flashlight%20at%20its%20brightest%20setting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFlashlight%20brightness%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20I%20used%20the%20same%20test%20we%20use%20for%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fbest-flashlight%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebest%20flashlight%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide.%20I%20shined%20the%20flashlight%20on%20its%20highest%20setting%20into%20one%20end%20of%20a%2042-inch-long%20box.%20The%20light%20reflected%20off%20the%20white%20surface%20on%20the%20other%20end%20of%20the%20box%2C%20and%20the%20light%20meter%20on%20the%20same%20side%20as%20the%20flashlight%20measured%20the%20lux%20output.%20I%20did%20it%20this%20way%20because%20you%20are%20likely%20to%20use%20a%20flashlight%20to%20reflect%20light%20off%20of%20objects%20you%E2%80%99re%20trying%20to%20see%2C%20rather%20than%20pointing%20it%20directly%20into%20your%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDurability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20radio%20blaring%2C%20I%20dropped%20each%20unit%20from%20a%20height%20of%207%20feet%20onto%20cement.%20Then%2C%20I%20observed%20any%20pieces%20that%20flew%20off%2C%20whether%20they%20were%20busted%20off%20for%20good%20or%20could%20be%20snapped%20back%20on%2C%20and%20if%20the%20radio%20continued%20to%20function%20well%20after%20the%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EUsability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20the%20help%20of%20my%2011-year-old%20son%2C%20I%20assessed%20how%20user-friendly%20each%20radio%20was%2C%20including%20portability%2C%20setting%20weather%20alerts%2C%20and%20adjusting%20the%20channel%2C%20band%2C%20and%20volume.%20If%20my%20kid%20could%20perform%20these%20tasks%20easily%2C%20then%20it%20was%20user-friendly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EExtra%20features%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20there%20were%20extra%20features%2C%20I%20made%20sure%20they%20worked%20as%20