0Tractor%20and%20L3Harris'%20AT-802U%20Sky%20Warden%2C%20designated%20the%20OA-1K%20Skyraider%20II%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-needs-more-than-new-fighters-bombers-win-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAFSOC%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20reference%20to%20the%20A-1%20Skyraiders%20of%20the%20Korean%20and%20Vietnam%20wars%2C%20is%20an%20armed%20intelligence%2C%20surveillance%2C%20and%20reconnaissance%2C%20close-air%20support%2C%20and%20strike%20aircraft%20that%20L3Harris%20says%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-studying-different-austere-bases-to-fight-in-pacific-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecan%20land%20almost%20anywhere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20light%20attack%20aircraft%20is%20a%20militarized%20variant%20of%20the%20Air%20Tractor%20AT-802%20long%20used%20for%20civilian%20work%20like%20agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20what%20it%20looks%20like%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20side%20of%20L3Harris'%20Sky%20Warden%20is%20seen%20sitting%20on%20an%20airfield%20with%20a%20grey%20overcast%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e1b07c6ad288d14808079%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EL3%20Harris%20representatives%20said%20one%20of%20the%20aircraft's%20highlights%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20operate%20and%20land%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20environments.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FChris%20Panella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20describes%20the%20Skyraider%20II%20as%20a%20flexible%20aircraft%20that%20can%20be%20adjusted%20for%20different%20missions%20and%20fights%2C%20noting%20that%20it%20has%20a%20much%20more%20manageable%20maintenance%20demand%20and%20a%20lower%20cost%20per%20flight%20hour%20than%20other%20AFSOC%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20its%20legendary%20predecessor%2C%20the%20new%20Skyraider%20was%20built%20for%20armed%20overwatch%20and%20attack%20in%20permissive%20environments%2C%20though%20the%20battlespace%20is%20not%20what%20it%20once%20was%2C%20and%20there%20are%20questions%20about%20its%20role%20in%20a%20high-intensity%20fight%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJon%20Rambeau%2C%20the%20president%20of%20integrated%20mission%20systems%20at%20L3Harris%2C%20said%20the%20Sky%20Warden%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bversatile%26quot%3B%20platform%20and%20%26quot%3Bcosts%20a%20fraction%20of%20what%20you%20might%20pay%20for%20a%20fighter%20jet.%26quot%3B%20Just%20how%20much%20the%20planes%20cost%20is%20a%20detail%20that%20isn't%20publicly%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERambeau%20and%20Clint%20Logwood%2C%20L3Harris'%20director%20of%20flight%20tests%20and%20flight%20operations%2C%20said%20one%20of%20Skyraider%20II's%20most%20important%20attributes%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20operate%20in%20different%20environments.%20It%20can%20also%20land%20just%20about%20anywhere%20with%20a%20limited%20logistics%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20right%20wing%20of%20L3Harris'%20Sky%20Warden%20plane%20is%20seen%20sitting%20on%20an%20airfield%20with%20an%20overcast%20sky%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e1b4fa466d2b74ab5834c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Sky%20Warden%2C%20or%20Skyraider%20II%2C%20can%20carry%20a%20host%20of%20weapons%20and%20communications%20systems.%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%2FChris%20Panella%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20thing%20could%20land%20anywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20Logwood%20said%2C%20from%20rugged%20and%20remote%20airfields%20to%20highways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20has%20prioritized%20flexibility%2C%20specifically%20the%20ability%20to%20operate%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fair-force-agile-combat-employment-means-new-tasks-for-airmen-2021-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eaustere%20environments%20and%20off%20of%20unconventional%20runways%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20roadways.%20Fixed%20airfields%20and%20bases%20are%20easy%20targets%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20where%20US%20forces%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20China's%20growing%20missile%20force%2C%20but%20an%20adversary%20can't%20target%20every%20piece%20of%20concrete%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELogwood%2C%20who%20has%20put%20many%20hours%20of%20testing%20the%20aircraft's%20capabilities%2C%20G-force%2C%20speed%2C%20temperature%2C%20and%20altitude%2C%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20landed%20this%20aircraft%20on%20some%20fields%20that%20would%20jar%20your%20teeth%2C%20and%20this%20aircraft%20just%20says%2C%20'That's%20all%20you%20got%3F'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sky%20Warden%20has%20%26quot%3Bplug%20and%20play%20technology%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20has%20a%20modular%20design%2C%20which%20means%20new%20systems%20can%20be%20quickly%20integrated%20into%20the%20aircraft.%20There%20are%20ten%20hardpoints%20capable%20of%20carrying%20a%20range%20of%20weapons%20and%20other%20technologies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20there%20are%20two%20seats%20in%20the%20Sky%20Warden%2C%20it's%20a%20single-pilot%20aircraft%20in%20which%20all%20of%20its%20systems%20are%20designed%20to%20be%20accessible%20by%20one%20person%20and%20easy%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222220%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22L3Harris'%20Sky%20Warden%20airplane%20is%20seen%20sitting%20on%20concrete%20with%20a%20cloudy%20sunset%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e1d91c6ad288d14808123%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221234%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EL3Harris%20said%20it%20has%20delivered%20multiple%20aircraft%20%26quot%3Bin%20quick%20succession%26quot%3B%20since%20last%20month.%3Cp%3EL3Harris%20Integrated%20Mission%20Systems%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20its%20cost-per-hour%20of%20flight%2C%20Rambeau%20said%2C%20is%20less%20than%20%241%2C000%20per%20hour%2C%20one%20of%20the%20cheaper%20cost%20estimates%20of%20the%20Air%20Force's%20fleet.%20He%20added%20that%20L3Harris%20was%20in%20conversation%20with%20potential%20international%20customers%20across%20the%20world%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBelow%20the%20wings%20of%20the%20Sky%20Warden%2C%20Logwood%20noted%2C%20were%20its%20dummy%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Farmy-testing-replacement-air-to-ground-hellfire-missile-2018-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAGM%20114%20Hellfire%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20as%20well%20as%20ISR%20sensors%20and%20arrays.%20If%20another%20mission%20pod%20is%20needed%2C%20it%20can%20be%20bolted%20and%20connected%20to%20the%20plane.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Sky%20Warden%20can%20be%20dissembled%20in%20under%20six%20hours%20and%20fit%20inside%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-wildly-overpaid-c-17-bathroom-soap-dispenser-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EC-17%20cargo%20aircraft%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20program%20was%20originally%20contracted%20for%2075%20aircraft%20in%20a%20%243%20billion%20deal%3B%20in%202023%20and%202024%2C%20the%20Government%20Accountability%20Office%20issued%20reports%20urging%20the%20Pentagon%20to%20reconsider%20the%20number%20of%20aircraft%20needed%2C%20citing%20concerns%20the%20program%20wouldn't%20be%20as%20valuable%20as%20the%20US%20shifts%20from%20decades%20of%20counterterrorism%20operations%20featuring%20air%20superiority%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fno-special-ops-easy-button-in-great-power-competition-expert-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enear-peer%20adversary%20fights%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERambeau%20cited%20the%20aircraft's%20potential%20international%20sales%20as%20examples%20%26quot%3Bto%20dispel%20the%20thought%20that%20this%20is%20only%20applicable%20for%20counterinsurgency%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20that%20those%20customers%20were%20looking%20at%20the%20aircraft%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20cockpit%20of%20L3Harris'%20Sky%20Warden%20aircraft%20is%20seen%20sitting%20on%20an%20airfield%20at%20night.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e1bfaa466d2b74ab58384%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20aircraft%20can%20host%20two%20pilots%20but%20is%20accessible%20for%20only%20one.%3Cp%3EL3Harris%20Integrated%20Missions%20Systems%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sky%20Warden%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20off%20and%20landing%20almost%20anywhere%2C%20Rambeau%20and%20Logwood%20said%20it%20would%20need%20to%20be%20modified%20for%20carrier-based%20operations.%20The%20aircraft%20requires%20a%20distance%20of%20about%201%2C200%20feet.%20For%20fighters%20and%20bombers%2C%20the%20required%20runway%20length%20tends%20to%20be%20thousands%20of%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20original%20Skyraider%20earned%20its%20legendary%20reputation%20by%20protecting%20downed%20airmen%20in%20Vietnam.%20Unlike%20jets%20that%20couldn't%20stay%20in%20the%20area%2C%20the%20Skyraiders%20could%20loiter%20for%20long%20periods%20of%20time%20and%20bring%20massive%20firepower%20for%20continuous%20suppressing%20fire%20until%20helicopters%20could%20come%20in%20for%20rescue%20operations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESkyraider%20pilot%20Maj.%20Bernard%20Fisher%20famously%20landed%20his%20plane%20through%20withering%20enemy%20fire%20at%20a%20battle-scarred%20airstrip%20littered%20with%20debris%20and%20destroyed%20aircraft%2C%20rescued%20a%20downed%20airman%2C%20and%20flew%20back%20out%20after%20taking%20multiple%20hits%20to%20his%20aircraft%20during%20a%201966%20fight%20at%20Ashau.%20Fisher%20received%20the%20Medal%20of%20Honor%20for%20his%20actions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Air%20Force%20is%20hoping%20the%20new%20Skyraiders%20will%20provide%20the%20same%20kind%20of%20exceptional%20support%20for%20troops%20in%20future%20fights.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-new-light-attack-aircraft-can-land-almost-anywhere-2025-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746815218000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F681e0adfc6ad288d14807cf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-new-light-attack-aircraft-can-land-almost-anywhere-2025-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22BI%20got%20a%20close%20look%20at%20the%20Sky%20Warden%2C%20or%20Skyraider%20II%2C%20attack%20airplane%20that%20was%20delivered%20to%20Air%20Force%20special%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cpanella%40businessinsider.com%20(Chris%20Panella)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A94%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-new-light-attack-aircraft-can-land-almost-anywhere-2025-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Told%20to%20pay%20more%20than%20brother%20for%20mom%E2%80%99s%20care%2C%20man%20moves%20HC%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1746814998000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-121044809%2Cimgsize-303064.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Ftold-to-pay-more-than-brother-for-moms-care-man-moves-hc%2Farticleshow%2F121038718.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22SAEED%20KHAN%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fahmedabad%2Ftold-to-pay-more-than-brother-for-moms-care-man-moves-hc%2Farticleshow%2F121038718.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22South%20Africa%20criticises%20US%20plan%20to%20accept%20white%20Afrikaners%20as%20refugees%